The activities they liked to do while travelling

Issues I came across in the project

Why I couldn’t use a chart that relies on a numerical factor

The numerical value that I recorded was not very compatable with the required secon graph that did not use geom_bar() as my numerical value recorded the TOTAL number of passengers on the vehicle and did not have a dynamic way of recording the count of the passengers. This led to multiple types of other graphs, such as box and whisker graphs, to appear as a single line with every entry of an observation using the same number of passengers.

Why I used geom_col() instead of geom_bar() for the Total People by Transport Type

As stated before, this current graph does not show the number of people taken into account. This was why the original graph used geom_col() rather than geom_bar().
